span.span: Defines an activity delegate that has seven in arguments and does not return a value.

remarks.format: ## Remarks 活动委托允许开发人员定义第三方在访问活动时需要指定的签名。An activity delegate allows a developer to define the required signature of an activity that will be specified by a third party. 此类型具有多个泛型版本，这些版本对所调用的活动采用 1 到 16 个自变量。There are multiple generic versions of this type that take from 1 to 16 arguments for the activity that is called. 此外，还有**ActivityFunc**的返回值的活动委托的类型。There are also **ActivityFunc** types for activity delegates that return values.
